These small droids are widespread. The term "utility droid" is used for many different models that varied widely in form and function. Some of them are at times referred as "astromech droids." 

Some models are used for advanced applied physics functions such as starship repair, astrogating, and even computer slicing and programming. Others perform more menial tasks such as janitorial duties and waste disposal.

Almost all are under one meter tall. They are equipped either with wheeled legs or small repulsorlift generators for movement, and painted the colours of their owner or simply left unadorned.

This woman seems to be a few screws lose of sanity. Her leg's and left arm are mostly robotic and seem to spark or smoke periodically. It seems her and the droids she sell have this in common. Although she seems to be crazy, her intentions and personality are quite nice.
